projects:
E-commerce Website with AI-Powered Personalization: Develop an e-commerce platform leveraging AI for personalized user experiences. Utilize machine learning algorithms to recommend products based on user behavior and preferences. Implement features like smart search, sentiment analysis for reviews, and chatbots for customer support. Portfolio Website with Interactive Data Visualization: Create a dynamic portfolio website showcasing projects and skills with interactive data visualization. Employ D3.js or Chart.js to present skills proficiency and project timelines. Include sections for projects, skills, education, and achievements, and integrate a blog for sharing insights. Prioritize responsive design, scalability, and security measures like HTTPS and encryption. Aim for a visually appealing and intuitive interface to captivate visitors and highlight your expertise effectively.
